<refentry id="crop.mode">
  <refmeta>
    <refentrytitle>crop.mode</refentrytitle>
  </refmeta>
  <refnamediv>
    <refname><parameter>crop.mode</parameter></refname>
    <refpurpose>How to display crops</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <programlisting>
      <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" parse="text" href="syn/crop.mode.xml"/></programlisting>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>Mode to pass to the crop package defining the form of the crops to
    display when <parameter>crop.marks</parameter> is not set to zero.</para>
    <para>The allowed values are detailed in the crop package manual.</para>
  </refsection>
